HedgeBoard is the “MyFxBook” of Crypto. It’s a Trading Performance Verification Tracking System. Using blockchain technology it’s able to record, store & secure all trading data of a traders portfolio & rate there performance using our complex algorithms to give the most accurate profile rating. This will verify all the self proclaimed Crypto Guru’s out there with our leader board. Every trade is recorded on the blockchain using smart contracts in real time. So no trader can go back & alter there records to look better. This is the only way to verify real traders & pay according to what there trades are really worth. Never pay for a losing trade again‼️ HedgeBoard incorporated a staking method to insure all costumers are guaranteed there purchase fee if the trade signal is a fail + commission.

node.text:
Artist @alonzovega2 decided to launch his first NFT collection on the @opensea website. They will be available at auction for only 2 weeks.

Cryptocurrency is needed to participate in this @NFT market, which you can acquire through investment brokers that are tailored to cryptocurrency trading, such as Webull and SoFi Active Invest. Each offers commission-free trading on individual stocks, exchange-traded funds (ETFs), and options.

node.text:
We never thought this would be possible -  but @Skeletonconceptofficial keeps proving us wrong. They have done the impossible and skeletonized the very complex GMT-MASTER II “Batman”.
 
The Concept is named after the French champion of the 2018 football World Cup and @psg player @kimpembe3, who participated in the creating process of this stunning timepiece with the Skeleton Concept’s team of master watchmakers.
 
The GMT Master II has been entirely redesigned to give it a sportswear character that would match the personality of Kimpembe. The blue of the bi-color bezel has been intensified as it is the footballer’s signature color. It has added more contrast to the movement as it fits perfectly with the gray matte Oyster Steel look of the original bracelet. 
 
Skeleton Concept added a special nod to the football player coloring the number 3 on the date module in blue - as it is his number on the football team!
 
This personalization is a World premiere. Fitting, for a World champion…
________
Skeleton Concept is a handcraft atelier that specializes in watch customization.
They neither manufacture and/or sell timepieces. Skeleton Concept is not affiliated, associated, authorized, endorsed by, or in any way officially connected with RoleX SA or any of its subsidiaries.  The personalization of the watches are carried out meticulously while staying true to the essence of the original brand manufacturers. Skeleton Concept assures the integrity of the work and modifications made on behalf of its clients and their timepieces. Any and all the customizations made are for the personal and private use of the owners only
